WEBVTT

00:00.701 --> 00:03.604
[ DRAMATIC MUSIC PLAYS ]

00:36.670 --> 00:38.406
YOU THINK I'M SCARED?

00:40.574 --> 00:42.510
THIS AIN'T SHIT.

00:42.510 --> 00:45.479
UNCUFF ME,
MOTHER [BLEEP]

00:45.479 --> 00:46.747
IT WASN'T ME.

00:46.747 --> 00:50.084
I SWEAR ON MY GRANDMOTHER,
IT WASN'T ME.

00:50.084 --> 00:51.885
JUST LET ME GO,
MOTHER [BLEEP]

00:51.885 --> 00:53.554
[ CAMERA SHUTTER CLICKS ]

00:53.554 --> 00:57.425
SOMETIMES COPS FIND A CASE
CAN DIG THEM INTO A HOLE.

00:57.425 --> 00:59.793
BEFORE SUNRISE,
DETECTIVE SAMMY BRYANT

00:59.793 --> 01:03.831
WILL DISCOVER JUST HOW HARD
IT CAN BE TO DIG YOURSELF OUT.

01:07.435 --> 01:10.671
I'M TELLING YOU,
THIS WAS AN AIRTIGHT CASE.

01:10.671 --> 01:12.039
IT COULD FLOAT.

01:12.039 --> 01:13.907
YEAH, RIGHT.
NOT IN THIS LINE OF BUSINESS.

01:13.907 --> 01:15.276
SO, THIS FOOL
KILLED THE GUY,

01:15.276 --> 01:16.677
AND HE'S STANDING
OVER THE DEAD BODY,

01:16.677 --> 01:18.546
TALKING CRAP TO THE DEAD BODY
RIGHT HERE.

01:18.546 --> 01:20.248
OH, HERE?

01:20.248 --> 01:22.783
SO, HE DROPS THE GUN
WHEN HE SEES THE ROOKIE
PULL UP IN THE U-BOAT.

01:22.783 --> 01:24.185
OH, WHO PULLED UP?
MURO?

01:24.185 --> 01:25.619
NICK ALBERT.

01:25.619 --> 01:27.821
OH, MAN, ALBERT -- HE COULD
MESS UP A ONE-CAR FUNERAL.

01:27.821 --> 01:29.523
EXACTLY.

01:29.523 --> 01:31.792
KIND OF MAKES YOU WONDER
WHO WAS SHAKING MORE,
HIM OR THE SUSPECT.

01:31.792 --> 01:35.095
[ CHUCKLES ]
SO, ALBERT ASKS THE GUY,
"WHAT HAPPENED?"

01:35.095 --> 01:36.664
AND THE GUY SAYS,
"I SHOT THE BASTARD."

01:36.664 --> 01:38.766
WOW.
OH, NO, NO,
BUT HERE'S THE PUNCHLINE.

01:38.766 --> 01:40.134
ALBERT DOESN'T
MIRANDIZE HIM.

01:40.134 --> 01:42.102
HE JUST HOOKS HIM UP,
PUTS HIM IN THE CAR,

01:42.102 --> 01:44.405
AND STARTS
INTERROGATING HIM.
OH, PLEASE,
YOU GOT TO BE KIDDING ME.

01:44.405 --> 01:46.807
WITHOUT A MIRANDA WARNING,
NONE OF IT IS ADMISSIBLE.

01:46.807 --> 01:48.942
I GUESS HE WAS SO EXCITED
TO MAKE THE MURDER ARREST,

01:48.942 --> 01:50.611
HE JUST FORGOT.

01:50.611 --> 01:52.546
GREAT. NOW THE COURT'S GONNA
THROW OUT ALBERT'S TESTIMONY.

01:52.546 --> 01:55.883
GONE, AND NOW ALL WE HAVE
IS NAOMI CHESTER.

01:55.883 --> 01:57.351
YOU KNOW WHAT SUCKS?

01:57.351 --> 01:59.653
A COP SEES A MURDER
AND CAN'T TALK ABOUT IT.

01:59.653 --> 02:01.855
SHE'S SUPPOSED TO BE
PRETTY RELIABLE.

02:01.855 --> 02:03.357
CASE STILL
HAS A CHANCE.

02:03.357 --> 02:04.625
[ KNOCK ON DOOR ]

02:10.631 --> 02:12.065
YOU'RE EARLY.

02:12.065 --> 02:13.767
NOW,
WHAT'S THE CALL TIME?

02:13.767 --> 02:17.538
AND DID THEY SEND A LIMO
OR JUST A TOWN CAR?

02:17.538 --> 02:19.773
OKAY.

02:19.773 --> 02:22.376
MAYBE NOT SO RELIABLE.

02:22.376 --> 02:24.912
[ INDISTINCT CONVERSATIONS ]

02:27.915 --> 02:29.917
MORE COFFEE?

02:29.917 --> 02:31.285
OH, NO, I'M FINE.

02:31.285 --> 02:33.454
THAT'S CERTAINLY TRUE.

02:33.454 --> 02:36.890
I GUESS YOUR PARTNER
WASN'T HUNGRY.

02:36.890 --> 02:39.427
UH...

02:39.427 --> 02:41.595
HE'S NOT MY PARTNER,
NOT FULLY.

02:41.595 --> 02:44.164
I'M --
I'M STILL A TRAINEE.

02:44.164 --> 02:45.366
SOUND THRILLED.

02:45.366 --> 02:48.702
YEAH. WELL,
I'M ALMOST DONE.

02:48.702 --> 02:50.738
HE'S TAUGHT ME A LOT,
ACTUALLY.

02:50.738 --> 02:53.841
I'M JUST, UH,
READY FOR MORE.

02:53.841 --> 02:55.809
JUST GIVE ME THE DAMN BALL,
YOU KNOW?

02:55.809 --> 02:58.646
[ CHUCKLES ] YEAH.
SLOW YOUR ROLL, KEYSHAWN.

02:58.646 --> 03:00.080
SURE YOU'LL GET
YOUR CHANCE.

03:00.080 --> 03:01.882
YOU WATCH FOOTBALL?

03:01.882 --> 03:04.285
HEY, I GOT TWO OLDER BROTHERS.
I DON'T REALLY HAVE A CHOICE.

03:04.285 --> 03:06.287
Man: KAYA,
3 NEEDS TABASCO SAUCE,

03:06.287 --> 03:08.656
AND 4 WANTED EGGS
WITH ONIONS, NOT CHEESE.

03:08.656 --> 03:10.724
I'M ON IT!
HE SOUNDS ANGRY.

03:10.724 --> 03:12.192
[ SCOFFS ] WHATEVER.

03:12.192 --> 03:14.795
IT'S NOT LIKE I EVEN
WANT THIS JOB.

03:14.795 --> 03:17.398
WHAT DO YOU WANT TO DO?
SING.

03:17.398 --> 03:18.899
BUT, UM,
CRIMINAL JUSTICE

03:18.899 --> 03:21.569
WILL PROBABLY END UP
PAYING THE BILLS,

03:21.569 --> 03:23.070
SO I'LL TRANSFER SOON.

03:23.070 --> 03:25.873
YOU GO TO LAW SCHOOL?
HELL NO.
ARE YOU KIDDING?

03:25.873 --> 03:28.909
MY DAD WOULD KILL ME.
HE'S A COP.

03:28.909 --> 03:30.678
YEAH.

03:30.678 --> 03:32.646
[ Chuckling ] YEAH.
I'LL BE BACK.

03:32.646 --> 03:34.448
I HOPE SO.

03:41.054 --> 03:42.723
[ BREATHING HEAVILY ]

03:46.860 --> 03:47.861
[ PILLS CLATTER ]

04:12.252 --> 04:16.223
[ TOILET FLUSHES ]

04:16.223 --> 04:18.559
[ BOTTLE CLATTERS ]

04:36.176 --> 04:39.179
[ BREATHES DEEPLY ]

04:39.179 --> 04:42.015
[ INDISTINCT CONVERSATIONS ]

04:42.015 --> 04:43.951
I WAS GONNA SEND A SEARCH PARTY.
YOU ALL RIGHT?

04:43.951 --> 04:46.019
A DRUNK AND DISORDERLY CALL
CAME OUT AROUND THE CORNER.

04:46.019 --> 04:47.355
I ALREADY BOUGHT IT.

04:47.355 --> 04:49.189
YOU DIDN'T EAT.

04:49.189 --> 04:50.491
UM...

04:50.491 --> 04:52.760
PAY THE GIRL.
LET'S ROLL.

04:54.595 --> 04:57.931
[ SIGHS ]
JUST, UH, KEEP THE CHANGE.

04:57.931 --> 05:00.033
OH, YOU DON'T WANT
YOUR RECEIPT?
NO, I'M ALL RIGHT.

05:00.033 --> 05:01.769
WELL, YOU KNOW WHAT?

05:01.769 --> 05:03.471
YOU MIGHT NEED IT.
[ CHUCKLES ]

05:03.471 --> 05:05.172
UH, YEAH.
[ CHUCKLES ] RIGHT.

05:05.172 --> 05:06.674
I GOTTA GO.

05:06.674 --> 05:09.510
WELL, BE CAREFUL OUT THERE
PROTECTIN' AND SERVIN',

05:09.510 --> 05:11.111
OFFICER...SHERMAN.

05:11.111 --> 05:14.348
YOU TOO...KAYA?

05:14.348 --> 05:15.416
KAYA.
KAYA.

05:15.416 --> 05:16.517
KAYA.
KAYA.

05:16.517 --> 05:18.786
[ CHUCKLES ]

05:21.722 --> 05:23.391
PETEY,
YOU WANT TO FLIP ONE?

05:23.391 --> 05:24.692
Petey: SURE.

05:26.226 --> 05:27.761
[ STOOL SCRAPES ]

05:27.761 --> 05:30.364
IT'S REALLY HOT,
SO DON'T TOUCH.

05:32.332 --> 05:33.701
OKAY.

05:35.969 --> 05:37.471
WHEN DO I FLIP IT?

05:37.471 --> 05:39.807
NOW'S GOOD.

05:39.807 --> 05:42.209
GOOD.

05:42.209 --> 05:43.511
WHO TAUGHT YOU?

05:43.511 --> 05:45.212
MY MOM.

05:45.212 --> 05:47.080
BUT THE REAL SECRET IS TO...

05:47.080 --> 05:48.982
marry a woman
who knows how to cook.

05:48.982 --> 05:53.186
MY DAD SAID
THE SAME THING.

05:53.186 --> 05:55.288
IS MOM UP YET?

05:55.288 --> 05:59.292
UH...NO.
UH, NOT YET.

05:59.292 --> 06:01.762
SHE WAS -- SHE WAS UP
WITH THE BABY.

06:01.762 --> 06:05.433
HOW MUCH LONGER
ARE YOU STAYING WITH US?

06:05.433 --> 06:09.603
I DON'T KNOW.
A WHILE, I GUESS.

06:09.603 --> 06:11.071
IS THAT ALL RIGHT
WITH YOU?

06:11.071 --> 06:14.842
MOM DOESN'T CRY AS MUCH
WHEN YOU'RE AROUND.

06:16.710 --> 06:20.180
[ CELLPHONE RINGS ]

06:20.180 --> 06:22.916
[ CELLPHONE BEEPS ]

06:22.916 --> 06:26.019
DETECTIVE BRYANT.

06:26.019 --> 06:27.555
10:30, OKAY.

06:27.555 --> 06:29.156
SEE YOU THEN.

06:29.156 --> 06:31.525
[ CELLPHONE BEEPS ]

06:31.525 --> 06:33.627
SOMETHING SMELLS GOOD!

06:33.627 --> 06:35.629
PANCAKES?
[ GASPS ]

06:35.629 --> 06:37.164
MY FAVORITE!

06:37.164 --> 06:40.568
HEY, CAN YOU TURN ON THE HEAT
BACK HERE?

06:40.568 --> 06:43.303
WHAT ARE YOU LOOKING AT?

06:43.303 --> 06:44.638
NOTHING.

06:44.638 --> 06:47.641
WHY ARE Y'ALL
SO QUIET?

06:47.641 --> 06:49.910
WATCHING "COPS,"
ALL Y'ALL DO IS DRIVE, YAP,

06:49.910 --> 06:51.612
TALK SHIT
ABOUT YOUR WIVES.

06:51.612 --> 06:53.614
WELL, THIS AIN'T TV.

06:53.614 --> 06:56.784
WHEW! I SENSE A LITTLE TENSION
BETWEEN YOU GUYS.

06:56.784 --> 06:59.520
WHAT? SOMEONE LEAVE
THE TOILET SEAT UP?

06:59.520 --> 07:00.721
AW, COME ON!
COME ON!

07:00.721 --> 07:02.155
[ SIREN CHIRPS ]

07:02.155 --> 07:04.157
PAY ATTENTION!

07:04.157 --> 07:07.695
IT'S COLDER THAN A WITCH'S TIT,
AND YOU ARE SWEATING BULLETS.

07:07.695 --> 07:11.765
ARE YOU HIGH?

07:11.765 --> 07:13.133
WHAT DID YOU SAY?

07:13.133 --> 07:15.469
MUST BE SOME STRONG SHIT.
CAN I GET SOME, TOO?

07:15.469 --> 07:16.837
[ TIRES SCREECH ]

07:16.837 --> 07:18.839
UGH!
[BLEEP] MY NOSE!

07:18.839 --> 07:21.041
AAH!
YOU BROKE MY NOSE!

07:21.041 --> 07:23.477
AAH!

07:23.477 --> 07:26.379
YOU [BLEEP] BROKE MY NOSE,
YOU PIGS!

07:26.379 --> 07:28.015
AAH!
JOHN! JOHN!

07:28.015 --> 07:30.651
ON THE RIGHT.
WHAT'S THAT ABOUT,
DUDE?!

07:30.651 --> 07:31.985
[ WOMAN CRYING ]

07:33.453 --> 07:34.722
YOU BROKE MY NOSE!

07:34.722 --> 07:36.189
MA'AM, WHAT'S WRONG?
YOU ALL RIGHT?

07:36.189 --> 07:38.425
THEY HAD GUNS!
GUNS!

07:38.425 --> 07:39.893
WHO DID?

07:39.893 --> 07:40.928
WHO?

07:40.928 --> 07:42.596
ALL RIGHT.
WHOA, WHOA, WHOA, WHOA!

07:42.596 --> 07:44.097
GUYS, GUYS, GUYS, COME ON.
BE SAFE.

07:44.097 --> 07:47.434
WHAT IS WRONG
WITH WHAT I HAVE ON?

07:47.434 --> 07:49.069
OH, YOU REALLY
HAVE TO ASK?

07:49.069 --> 07:50.838
WE DON'T HAVE TIME
FOR THIS.

07:50.838 --> 07:52.873
NO, LISTEN, WE CANNOT
HAVE HER TESTIFY

07:52.873 --> 07:54.975
LOOKING LIKE
THE FOURTH CHARLIE'S ANGEL.

07:54.975 --> 07:56.644
I GUESTED
ON "CHARLIE'S ANGELS" --

07:56.644 --> 07:58.078
A COUPLE OF TIMES.

07:58.078 --> 08:00.581
THEY DIDN'T HAVE ME BACK,
THOUGH.

08:00.581 --> 08:03.817
LOOK, WE HAVE TO
COVER YOUR CHICHIS.

08:03.817 --> 08:05.719
IF YOU'VE GOT IT,
FLAUNT IT.

08:05.719 --> 08:07.354
WHO'S PAYING FOR THIS?

08:07.354 --> 08:09.923
HEY, WE GET THE CONVICTION,
FERNANDEZ IS GONNA REIMBURSE US.

08:09.923 --> 08:11.992
GOING ON YOUR CARD,
NOT MINE.

08:11.992 --> 08:15.462
OH, NO, NO, NO, NO.
THIS IS A 50/50 SPLIT, PARTNER.

08:15.462 --> 08:17.698
HEY, LOOK,
MEMORY IS A FRAGILE THING,

08:17.698 --> 08:20.534
AND YOU HAD AN INCREDIBLY
TRAUMATIC EXPERIENCE.

08:20.534 --> 08:22.936
DON'T BEAT YOURSELF UP
ABOUT IT.

08:22.936 --> 08:25.673
SO, NOW WHAT?

08:25.673 --> 08:28.075
WE'RE WORKING
SEVERAL OTHER ANGLES.

08:28.075 --> 08:29.476
SOMETHING WILL BREAK.

08:29.476 --> 08:30.611
YEAH.

08:32.479 --> 08:35.683
LISTEN,
LET'S GET THIS STRAIGHT.

08:35.683 --> 08:37.951
A POLICE OFFICER WAS KILLED,
DETECTIVE.

08:37.951 --> 08:40.854
NO ONE IN THIS DEPARTMENT
IS GIVING UP

08:40.854 --> 08:44.658
ON CATCHING THE MEN
WHO KILLED YOUR PARTNER.

08:44.658 --> 08:46.193
UH, UM...

08:46.193 --> 08:48.829
A WITNESS FROM ANOTHER CASE
JUST SHOWED UP.

08:48.829 --> 08:50.297
UH, CAN YOU GIVE ME
A FEW MOMENTS?
THANK YOU.

08:50.297 --> 08:52.165
OKAY.
[ CLEARS THROAT ]

08:52.165 --> 08:53.767
Hey...

09:23.764 --> 09:25.899
[ CAMERA SHUTTER CLICKS ]

09:27.901 --> 09:30.137
[ TELEPHONE RINGING ]

09:33.674 --> 09:37.477
STEALING FIELD-TRIP MONEY
FROM LITTLE KIDS --

09:37.477 --> 09:39.446
THAT IS SOME TWISTED...

09:39.446 --> 09:40.714
TELL YOU SOMETHING,
MAN.

09:40.714 --> 09:42.215
TWO 13-YEAR-OLDS
WITH 9-MILLIMETERS?

09:42.215 --> 09:43.784
YOU GOT TO LOVE
THE GHETTO.

09:43.784 --> 09:45.318
WELL, MAKES SENSE.
UNARMED FOURTH GRADERS.

09:45.318 --> 09:47.354
WHAT ARE THEY GONNA DO,
THROW A TRANSFORMER AT SOMEBODY?

09:47.354 --> 09:49.823
WHERE THE HELL'S OPTIMUS PRIME
WHEN YOU NEED HIM?

09:49.823 --> 09:51.291
YEAH.
RIGHT.

09:51.291 --> 09:53.661
I'LL BE RIGHT BACK.
I'M GONNA GRAB A COFFEE.

09:56.029 --> 09:57.798
SORRY ABOUT
THE OTHER DAY.

09:57.798 --> 10:00.634
YOU ALL RIGHT?

10:00.634 --> 10:02.135
IT'S LIKE COOP SAYS.

10:02.135 --> 10:05.806
IF I'M NOT OUT HERE,
WHO ELSE IS IT GONNA BE?

10:05.806 --> 10:07.507
IS HE ALL RIGHT?

10:07.507 --> 10:09.576
EH, HARD TO TELL.

10:09.576 --> 10:11.845
NOT IF YOUR EYES
ARE OPEN.

10:11.845 --> 10:14.214
HE'S MY TRAINING OFFICER,
CHICKIE.
OKAY.

10:14.214 --> 10:16.216
WELL, RANK DOESN'T MATTER
IF YOU'RE DEAD.

10:16.216 --> 10:20.821
YOU GOT TO BE ABLE TO TRUST
THE GUY WATCHING YOUR BACK...

10:20.821 --> 10:24.224
NO MATTER WHO IT IS.

10:24.224 --> 10:26.326
HEY, LET ME OUT...
Officer: SHUT UP!

10:28.762 --> 10:30.230
WHAT'S UP?

10:30.230 --> 10:33.066
I DON'T THINK THAT KID
WAS ON THE BUS.

10:38.638 --> 10:41.141
HEY.

10:41.141 --> 10:42.609
HEY,
WHAT'S YOUR NAME?

10:42.609 --> 10:43.944
MICHAEL.

10:43.944 --> 10:46.914
HEY, MICHAEL.
I'M JOHN.

10:46.914 --> 10:50.417
WERE YOU, UH -- WERE YOU
ON THAT BUS THAT GOT ROBBED?

10:50.417 --> 10:52.019
NO.

10:52.019 --> 10:54.121
NO?

10:54.121 --> 10:56.289
DO YOU GO TO SCHOOL,
MICHAEL?

10:58.558 --> 11:00.961
DO YOU KNOW
WHO ROBBED IT?

11:00.961 --> 11:04.765
DID YOU SEE IT HAPPEN?

11:04.765 --> 11:06.734
WHERE ARE YOUR PARENTS,
MICHAEL?

11:06.734 --> 11:09.737
GONE.
YOU GONNA TAKE ME TO JAIL?

11:09.737 --> 11:12.639
NO.
NO, OF COURSE NOT.

11:12.639 --> 11:14.441
WHERE DO YOU LIVE,
THOUGH, MICHAEL?

11:14.441 --> 11:15.542
WHAT'S YOUR ADDRESS?

11:15.542 --> 11:18.045
THE MAGIC CAVE.

11:18.045 --> 11:21.081
OKEY DOKEY SMOKEY MAKES US
HIDE IN THE MAGIC CAVE

11:21.081 --> 11:23.350
SO THEY DON'T
TAKE US TO JAIL.

11:23.350 --> 11:25.753
OKAY.

11:25.753 --> 11:28.255
Go get the paramedics.

11:32.893 --> 11:34.962
ACCORDING TO
THE FINGERPRINT DATABASE,

11:34.962 --> 11:37.731
MICHAEL PETERSON
IS 9 YEARS OLD.

11:37.731 --> 11:40.233
9? HE LOOKS 6.

11:40.233 --> 11:42.269
MALNUTRITION PROBABLY
STUNTED HIS GROWTH.

11:42.269 --> 11:44.604
HE WAS IN THE SYSTEM?
MM-HMM.

11:44.604 --> 11:46.173
PARENTS
SHOULD BE SHOT.

11:46.173 --> 11:49.642
WELL, HIS FATHER'S AT FOLSOM,
AND HIS MOTHER'S DEAD.

11:49.642 --> 11:50.844
SHE WAS A PROSTITUTE.

11:50.844 --> 11:52.545
WHERE'S MICHAEL BEEN?

11:52.545 --> 11:55.115
NO OTHER RELATIVES, SO HE'S BEEN
AT A FOSTER HOME OVER ON 89th.

11:55.115 --> 11:57.717
WENT MISSING
ABOUT THREE WEEKS AGO.

11:57.717 --> 11:58.886
THREE WEEKS?

11:58.886 --> 12:00.720
WHAT, NO AMBER ALERT?

12:00.720 --> 12:02.122
WE'VE BEEN LOOKING.

12:02.122 --> 12:04.091
RIGHT.

12:06.059 --> 12:08.528
TALKED ABOUT
A MAGIC CAVE.

12:08.528 --> 12:12.232
KIDS AT THAT AGE LIKE TO IMAGINE
ANY SMALL SPACE AS A CAVE.

12:12.232 --> 12:14.034
HE'S AT A PRE-OPERATIONAL
STATE OF DEVELOPMENT.

12:14.034 --> 12:15.535
PRE-OPERATIONAL?

12:15.535 --> 12:18.105
YOU JUST TOLD ME THE KID
WAS ALONE FOR THREE WEEKS.

12:18.105 --> 12:19.940
HE MENTIONED
TWO OTHER KIDS, ALSO.

12:19.940 --> 12:22.042
HE'S PROBABLY
MAKING IT UP.

12:22.042 --> 12:24.511
I'VE DONE HUNDREDS
OF THESE CASES.

12:24.511 --> 12:27.080
I DON'T NEED THE M.E. TO TELL ME
MICHAEL'S BEEN ABUSED.

12:27.080 --> 12:28.381
BUT A KID THIS TRAUMATIZED
WILL ENGAGE

12:28.381 --> 12:29.749
IN ALL SORTS
OF MAGICAL THINKING...

12:29.749 --> 12:30.984
YOU KNOW,
HE WAS PRETTY SPECIFIC.

12:30.984 --> 12:32.285
...AS A SELF-PROTECTIVE
MECHANISM.

12:32.285 --> 12:34.221
I UNDERSTAND THAT.
HE WAS SPECIFIC, THOUGH.

12:34.221 --> 12:35.989
CALLED THEM BY NAME --
TYRELL AND ANDY.

12:35.989 --> 12:37.524
LOOK, I-I APPRECIATE

12:37.524 --> 12:40.493
THE GREAT WORK THAT YOU'VE DONE
IN SPOTTING HIM.

12:40.493 --> 12:43.230
OKAY? I REALLY DO.
BUT NOW IT'S MY CASE.

12:43.230 --> 12:45.232
AND EXPERT CARE IS WHAT
THIS CHILD NEEDS.

12:45.232 --> 12:46.800
EXPERT CARE?
WHAT EXPERT? YOU?

12:46.800 --> 12:49.769
I HAVE A MASTER'S DEGREE
IN CHILD PSYCHOLOGY.

12:49.769 --> 12:51.304
AND I GOT A PhD IN STREET.
WHO GIVES A SHIT?

12:51.304 --> 12:53.240
AND 20 YEARS'
EXPERIENCE.
OH, 20 YEARS!

12:53.240 --> 12:54.674
YOU KNOW WHAT?!
I DON'T CARE!

12:54.674 --> 12:56.143
THAT KID
IS TELLING THE TRUTH,

12:56.143 --> 12:57.911
AND YOU'RE TOO [BLEEP] LAZY
TO DO YOUR JOB!

12:57.911 --> 13:00.413
JOHN!
DO YOUR [BLEEP] JOB!

13:02.382 --> 13:03.951
MIKE WAS A GOOD GUY.

13:03.951 --> 13:06.453
HE DIDN'T DESERVE
TO GET SHOT.

13:06.453 --> 13:10.891
YOU KNOW, WHAT HAPPENS BETWEEN
A MAN AND ANOTHER MAN'S WIFE

13:10.891 --> 13:15.963
IS NOBODY'S BUSINESS,
ESPECIALLY HER HUSBAND'S.

13:15.963 --> 13:17.764
WE, UH -- WE APPRECIATE
YOU DOING THIS.

13:17.764 --> 13:20.300
WHEN DO WE DO THIS?
IT'S AT 3:00.

13:20.300 --> 13:23.937
I -- I THOUGHT
IT WAS THIS MORNING.

13:23.937 --> 13:26.039
TOOLEY WAS
A MISS-OUT.
WHAT?

13:26.039 --> 13:28.008
HE MISSED THE BUS
FROM JAIL TO COURT.

13:28.008 --> 13:31.511
THERE WON'T BE ANOTHER ONE
TILL AT LEAST NOON.

13:31.511 --> 13:34.414
YOU OKAY WITH THAT?

13:34.414 --> 13:35.748
SURE.

13:35.748 --> 13:38.051
GREAT. YOU'RE GONNA DO
JUST FINE, NAOMI. I KNOW IT.

13:38.051 --> 13:40.387
CAN YOU, UH, EXCUSE ME
FOR A MOMENT?

13:40.387 --> 13:43.156
COUNSELOR, CAN I SPEAK TO YOU,
PLEASE?

13:43.156 --> 13:48.929
OH, MAN, MAN.
THAT IS FOUR HOURS FROM NOW.

13:48.929 --> 13:52.765
I CANNOT GO THAT LONG...

13:52.765 --> 13:55.302
WITHOUT MY MEDICATION.

13:55.302 --> 13:57.070
THAT WOMAN'S
A STRAIGHT-UP DRUNK.

13:57.070 --> 13:58.505
I DON'T THINK
SHE'S GONNA MAKE IT.

13:58.505 --> 14:00.340
WELL, SHE BETTER.

14:00.340 --> 14:02.709
SHE'S GONNA NEED TO
GET SOMETHING SOON.

14:02.709 --> 14:05.112
[ SIGHS ]

14:05.112 --> 14:08.448
LOOK, LEGALLY, I CAN'T MAKE
ANY SUGGESTIONS.

14:08.448 --> 14:11.418
BUT A HAPPY WITNESS
IS A COOPERATIVE WITNESS.

14:11.418 --> 14:13.253
CATCH MY DRIFT?

14:15.522 --> 14:16.489
[ SIGHS ]

14:32.872 --> 14:36.509
[ CELLPHONE RINGS ]

14:36.509 --> 14:37.777
[ CELLPHONE BEEPS ]

14:37.777 --> 14:39.412
HEY.

14:39.412 --> 14:40.413
MARIELLA?

14:40.413 --> 14:43.750
CALM DOWN.

14:43.750 --> 14:46.686
I'LL BE RIGHT THERE.

14:46.686 --> 14:48.956
[ CELLPHONE BEEPS ]

15:02.635 --> 15:06.406
McBRIDE FROM SEX CRIMES
HAS IT COVERED.

15:06.406 --> 15:08.841
SO WHAT?

15:08.841 --> 15:11.078
SHE'S GOOD AT TAKING TESTS,
RIGHT?

15:11.078 --> 15:14.214
THAT'S ALL IT TAKES
TO BE A DETECTIVE.

15:14.214 --> 15:15.782
SHE DOESN'T KNOW
THE STREETS.

15:15.782 --> 15:18.986
DISPATCHER: A-43, possible 459,
suspects there now --

15:18.986 --> 15:21.221
4478 Vance Street.

15:21.221 --> 15:23.090
A-43 --
UNABLE TO RESPOND.

15:23.090 --> 15:24.958
SHOW US CODE 6.

15:24.958 --> 15:27.560
WE'RE NOT BUYING
THE CALL?

15:27.560 --> 15:30.297
NOPE.

15:30.297 --> 15:32.632
WE'RE NOT GONNA RESPOND
TO A BURGLARY CALL?

15:32.632 --> 15:34.467
YOU QUESTIONING
MY INSTINCTS, TOO?

15:34.467 --> 15:36.003
YES!
OH, REALLY?

15:36.003 --> 15:38.005
NOW YOU'RE THE [BLEEP] MAN,
HUH?

15:38.005 --> 15:39.506
WHAT WE'RE GONNA DO,
BOOT,

15:39.506 --> 15:41.541
IS WE'RE GONNA ROLL AROUND
ALL DAY,

15:41.541 --> 15:43.310
AND WE'RE GONNA SHOW THE [BLEEP]
KID'S PICTURE TO EVERYONE --

15:43.310 --> 15:44.711
ANYONE WHO'LL
LOOK AT IT!

15:44.711 --> 15:46.546
WE'RE NOT GONNA CHASE
THE GODDAMN RADIO!

15:46.546 --> 15:48.015
SO,
YOU RESPECT MY STRIPES,

15:48.015 --> 15:49.482
OR YOU GET THE [BLEEP]
OUT OF MY CAR!

15:52.385 --> 15:54.321
OBVIOUSLY, HE'S DEAD.
I'M HIS WIFE.
I UNDERSTAND.

15:54.321 --> 15:56.923
AND I'M HIS WIFE.
YES. MA'AM...

15:56.923 --> 15:59.993
SHE WON'T TRANSFER THE MONEY
FROM NATE'S SAVINGS ACCOUNT
INTO OUR CHECKING ACCOUNT.

15:59.993 --> 16:01.461
I'M SORRY,
MRS. MORETTA.

16:01.461 --> 16:03.830
I'VE EXPLAINED THE SITUATION
AS CLEARLY AS I CAN.

16:03.830 --> 16:05.432
WELL,
EXPLAIN IT TO ME.

16:05.432 --> 16:08.301
I NEED AN ORIGINAL COPY OF
MR. MORETTA'S DEATH CERTIFICATE.

16:08.301 --> 16:09.869
AND WHAT'S THAT
RIGHT THERE?

16:09.869 --> 16:11.171
IT'S A PRINTOUT
FROM A PDF.

16:11.171 --> 16:12.605
[ BREATHING
UNSTEADILY ]

16:12.605 --> 16:15.508
CAN YOU WAIT OUTSIDE
FOR A SECOND?

16:15.508 --> 16:17.077
[ SNIFFLES ]

16:21.114 --> 16:24.017
THAT'S THE WIFE
OF MY PARTNER.

16:24.017 --> 16:27.654
OKAY, HE WAS KILLED PROTECTING
YOUR RIGHT TO GIVE HER SHIT.

16:27.654 --> 16:29.489
I'M A RESERVIST.

16:29.489 --> 16:31.091
I DIDN'T LOSE THIS FINGER
IN THE KITCHEN.

16:31.091 --> 16:32.192
SO, THEN, YOU UNDERSTAND
WHAT IT'S LIKE

16:32.192 --> 16:33.793
TO SEE A FRIEND KILLED.

16:33.793 --> 16:36.163
YOUR WORLD STANDS STILL.
THE REST OF THE WORLD MOVES ON.

16:36.163 --> 16:37.397
NO ONE SEEMS TO CARE.

16:37.397 --> 16:39.532
I SYMPATHIZE
WITH MRS. MORETTA.

16:39.532 --> 16:40.800
I DO.

16:40.800 --> 16:42.302
BUT RULES ARE RULES.

16:42.302 --> 16:44.337
I RESPECT YOUR RULES.

16:44.337 --> 16:46.206
I DO.
I RESPECT YOUR RULES.

16:46.206 --> 16:48.075
BUT I'M ASKING YOU
FOR A FAVOR,

16:48.075 --> 16:50.710
FROM ONE SERVANT
TO ANOTHER.

16:54.781 --> 16:56.416
I'LL DO THE TRANSFER,

16:56.416 --> 17:01.488
BUT I'LL NEED AN ORIGINAL COPY
BY MORNING.

17:01.488 --> 17:03.556
THANK YOU.

17:06.959 --> 17:09.096
[ CRYING ]

17:10.997 --> 17:13.233
HEY,
IT'S GONNA BE OKAY.

17:13.233 --> 17:16.303
I'M GONNA GO DOWNTOWN,
GET HIS DOCUMENTS TOGETHER,

17:16.303 --> 17:18.705
AND I'LL BRING
THE PAPERWORK BACK HERE.

17:18.705 --> 17:20.340
OKAY?

17:26.179 --> 17:30.417
THANK YOU SO MUCH.
THANK YOU.

17:30.417 --> 17:33.953
I'M GONNA GET THIS GUY.
I PROMISE.

17:33.953 --> 17:35.322
WHAT?

17:38.425 --> 17:41.094
WE'RE GONNA GET HIM.

17:41.094 --> 17:42.895
OKAY.

17:42.895 --> 17:44.731
WE'RE GONNA GET HIM.
OKAY.

17:44.731 --> 17:47.234
I PROMISE.
ALL RIGHT.

17:47.234 --> 17:49.001
[ SNIFFLES ]

17:49.001 --> 17:50.537
I PROMISE.

17:54.707 --> 17:57.344
THIS LADY HAS GOT STORIES
FOR DAYS.

17:57.344 --> 17:58.578
OOH.
SHE LOOKS BEAUTIFUL
RIGHT THERE.

17:58.578 --> 18:01.214
I BET IF WE GAVE HER
THAT DRINK,

18:01.214 --> 18:02.582
IT WOULD REALLY
GET STARTED.

18:02.582 --> 18:06.119
HEY. 2:12 --
WE GOT TO GET BACK TO COURT.

18:06.119 --> 18:07.520
MM.
YOU GET LUNCH.

18:07.520 --> 18:09.789
OH, WHAT HAPPENED
TO "50/50, PARTNER"?

18:09.789 --> 18:11.057
[ SCOFFS ]

18:11.057 --> 18:14.394
HOW LONG HAS SHE BEEN
IN THE BATHROOM?

18:16.129 --> 18:17.497
SHIT! SHIT!

18:22.635 --> 18:25.838
OH! I'LL BET
SHE WENT OUT BACK!

18:25.838 --> 18:28.175
[ INDISTINCT CONVERSATIONS ]

18:31.744 --> 18:34.681
HEY! HEY, NAOMI!

18:34.681 --> 18:37.850
[ BOTH WHISTLE ]

18:37.850 --> 18:39.219
[ GROANS ]

18:39.219 --> 18:41.254
SHIT. OKAY, LOOK...
I'LL GET THE CAR.

18:42.722 --> 18:44.957
Ben: SEГ‘OR, SEГ‘OR.
PERDГіNAME.

18:44.957 --> 18:48.060
ВїHAS VISTO ESTE NIГ‘O?

18:48.060 --> 18:50.663
HMM? NO?

18:50.663 --> 18:53.099
EXCUSE ME.

18:53.099 --> 18:54.701
YOU SEEN THIS KID?

18:54.701 --> 18:58.605
CAN'T SAY THAT I HAVE.
IS HE OKAY?

18:58.605 --> 19:02.309
YEAH, HE IS NOW.
THANK YOU.

19:02.309 --> 19:04.444
WHAT ARE YOU
LOOKING FOR?

19:04.444 --> 19:06.112
HE WAS FOUND
IN THE AREA.

19:06.112 --> 19:08.681
WE'RE JUST TRYING TO BACKTRACK,
FIND OUT A HISTORY.

19:08.681 --> 19:10.550
WITH ALL THE GANGS
OUT HERE,

19:10.550 --> 19:13.085
YOU DON'T REALLY SEE KIDS
MUCH ANYMORE.

19:13.085 --> 19:15.655
I WISH I COULD BE
MORE HELPFUL.

19:18.057 --> 19:19.792
THANK YOU.

19:26.666 --> 19:28.735
[ BEN SIGHS ]

19:28.735 --> 19:31.471
HOW LONG ARE WE
GONNA KEEP DOING THIS?

19:31.471 --> 19:33.606
THEY'RE GONNA START
LOOKING FOR US.

19:35.808 --> 19:39.379
OH, COME ON.
WHAT THE HELL ARE YOU DOING?

19:39.379 --> 19:42.081
WHAT DOES IT LOOK LIKE?
GETTING MY SWERVE ON.

19:42.081 --> 19:43.450
UGH!

19:43.450 --> 19:46.453
AW, WHAT THE HELL, LADY?
LOOK AT THIS MESS.

19:46.453 --> 19:47.520
AHH!
DAMN IT!

19:47.520 --> 19:49.021
I'M CALLING THE COPS.

19:49.021 --> 19:51.691
HEY!
WE ARE THE COPS, OKAY?

19:51.691 --> 19:53.493
COME ON,
GET OUT OF HERE.

19:53.493 --> 19:55.795
SORRY ABOUT THAT.
YEAH, SURE.

19:55.795 --> 19:58.331
Chuck:
HOW LONG YOU NEED IT?
COUPLE OF DAYS.

19:58.331 --> 20:00.867
WE NEED ANOTHER DECOY
FOR A SURVEILLANCE.

20:00.867 --> 20:02.302
IT DOESN'T MATTER TO ME.

20:02.302 --> 20:04.304
EVERYTHING YOU SEE IN HERE
IS GONNA GET CRUSHED

20:04.304 --> 20:05.838
IN THE NEXT FEW DAYS,
ANYWAY.

20:05.838 --> 20:09.576
IT'S A WASTE OF AMERICAN
INGENUITY, IF YOU ASK ME.

20:13.346 --> 20:14.781
THEY'LL BE READY FOR YOU
ANY MINUTE.

20:14.781 --> 20:16.616
OH, GOD.
I CAN'T DO THIS!

20:16.616 --> 20:18.351
OH, LISTEN, LISTEN.
LOOK, HE CAN'T HURT YOU.

20:18.351 --> 20:19.686
WE'RE RIGHT HERE.

20:19.686 --> 20:22.355
YEAH. TOOLEY SHOT MIKE DOWN
LIKE A DOG.

20:22.355 --> 20:24.156
TOOLEY DID THAT
TO MAKE A STATEMENT.

20:24.156 --> 20:27.059
WELL, HE MADE A STATEMENT,
ALL RIGHT. I GET THE MESSAGE.

20:27.059 --> 20:29.896
OKAY, LISTEN --
GOD, I DON'T KNOW
WHAT THE HELL I WAS THINKING.

20:29.896 --> 20:31.464
YOU KNOW WHAT?

20:31.464 --> 20:33.466
YOU DON'T STRIKE ME AS THE TYPE
TO GET SCARED VERY EASILY,

20:33.466 --> 20:34.734
SO WHY NOW?

20:37.169 --> 20:42.008
I WAS FLATTERED
WHEN THEY ASKED ME TO TESTIFY.

20:43.976 --> 20:46.313
SILLY, AIN'T IT?

20:46.313 --> 20:50.317
IT'S JUST BEEN SO LONG
SINCE...

20:50.317 --> 20:52.885
ANYBODY WANTED ANYTHING
FROM ME.

20:52.885 --> 20:54.421
[ SCOFFS ]

20:54.421 --> 20:59.025
BUT I DIDN'T THINK I WOULD
REALLY HAVE TO REALLY DO IT.

20:59.025 --> 21:02.629
YEAH, BUT HERE WE ARE,
AND YOU SPEAK FOR MIKE.

21:02.629 --> 21:05.598
AND EVERYBODY WANTS TO HEAR
WHAT YOU HAVE TO SAY.

21:05.598 --> 21:08.368
THIS IS THE BIGGEST SHOW
IMAGINABLE.

21:08.368 --> 21:11.037
AND THEY'RE GONNA BE
HANGING ON EVERY WORD.

21:11.037 --> 21:14.173
NOT ONLY IS THIS
THE ROLE OF A LIFETIME,

21:14.173 --> 21:15.708
BUT THERE'S NO WAY

21:15.708 --> 21:17.710
THAT THEY'LL EVER, EVER
BE ABLE TO CUT YOU OUT.

21:17.710 --> 21:20.980
AND IF YOU DON'T TALK,
TOOLEY SKATES.

21:20.980 --> 21:23.883
Bailiff: THEY'RE READY FOR YOU,
MS. CHESTER.

21:36.028 --> 21:40.232
SHARPSHOOTIN' DAVE.
HOW ARE YOU, MAN?

21:40.232 --> 21:41.968
JOHNNY.

21:41.968 --> 21:45.137
HEY, KID.

21:45.137 --> 21:49.442
HOW'S THE DYNAMIC DUO?

21:49.442 --> 21:51.811
UH-OH.

21:51.811 --> 21:53.980
SOMEONE PEE
IN YOUR CORNFLAKES?

21:55.448 --> 21:58.751
HEY, IT ALL RIGHT, MAN.
YOU KNOW HOW IT IS.

21:58.751 --> 22:02.221
KID'S SALTY --
USED TO HANG ON YOUR EVERY WORD.

22:02.221 --> 22:04.323
NOW HE'S SMELLING
HIS OWN PISS,

22:04.323 --> 22:06.993
LOOKING AT YOU
LIKE YOU'RE THE ASSHOLE.

22:06.993 --> 22:09.095
[ SIGHS ]

22:09.095 --> 22:12.298
FATHERHOOD, MAN.

22:12.298 --> 22:15.735
NATURAL COURSE
OF THINGS.

22:15.735 --> 22:18.971
YOU KNOW, IF HE DIDN'T CHAFE
AND BUCK UP AGAINST YOU,

22:18.971 --> 22:21.941
YOU WOULDN'T KNOW YOU WERE
TURNING HIM INTO A GOOD COP.

22:21.941 --> 22:23.410
NOW YOU KNOW.

22:23.410 --> 22:25.612
[ WATER RUNS ]

22:30.717 --> 22:34.020
YOU ALL RIGHT, MAN?

22:34.020 --> 22:37.857
WHY DON'T YOU LAY OFF THAT SHIT?
YOU DON'T LOOK SO GOOD.

22:39.626 --> 22:42.228
YOU SHOULD COME WITH ME
TO A MEETING.

22:42.228 --> 22:44.897
YOU SHOULD KISS MY ASS.

22:48.435 --> 22:53.906
MIKE HAD HIS --
HIS HANDS IN THE AIR.

22:53.906 --> 22:55.341
HE WAS SHAKING.

22:55.341 --> 22:58.945
HE WAS PLEADING
WITH TOOLEY,

22:58.945 --> 23:03.349
"COME ON, LOOK, MAN,
I'M -- I'M -- I'M SORRY."

23:03.349 --> 23:07.286
BUT TOOLEY JUST WALKED
CLOSER TO HIM.

23:07.286 --> 23:11.624
HE PUT THE GUN TO HIS HEAD,
AND HE BLEW HIM BACK.

23:11.624 --> 23:14.393
MIKE WAS LAYING
ON THE GROUND.

23:14.393 --> 23:18.330
HIS --
HIS LEGS WERE TWITCHING.

23:18.330 --> 23:20.933
TOOLEY STOOD OVER HIM,
LAUGHING.

23:20.933 --> 23:24.403
HE STILL HAD THE GUN
IN HIS HAND.

23:24.403 --> 23:26.773
HE LOOKED AT MIKE,
AND HE SAID,

23:26.773 --> 23:29.408
"GUESS WHO JUST GOT FU--"
OH.

23:29.408 --> 23:30.510
[ FEEDBACK WHINES ]

23:30.510 --> 23:31.911
Excuse my language,
judge.

23:31.911 --> 23:33.546
Is it okay if I say that
in court?

23:33.546 --> 23:35.047
Judge:
YOU MAY CONTINUE.

23:40.820 --> 23:44.323
"GUESS WHO JUST GOT [BLEEP]"

23:44.323 --> 23:46.793
Damn.

23:46.793 --> 23:50.597
She does have presence.

23:50.597 --> 23:52.031
YOU DID GOOD, KID.

23:52.031 --> 23:54.400
ALL RIGHT, WHERE DO YOU
WANT TO GO TO DINNER?

23:54.400 --> 23:56.503
MY PICK?
IT'S ON THE STATE.

23:56.503 --> 23:58.905
PACIFIC DINING CAR.

23:58.905 --> 24:00.306
OOH. OOH.

24:00.306 --> 24:01.407
SNAP!

24:01.407 --> 24:02.542
[ LAUGHTER ]

24:02.542 --> 24:05.211
GO HOME, BEN.

24:07.013 --> 24:09.415
JUST TELL ME WHY.

24:09.415 --> 24:12.051
WHAT ABOUT THIS KID
MAKES IT WORTH LOSING YOUR JOB.

24:12.051 --> 24:15.888
KID'S TELLING THE TRUTH.
I FEEL IT.

24:15.888 --> 24:18.858
SO, WHAT'S THE PLAN?
THERE IS NONE.

24:18.858 --> 24:21.761
JUST GONNA GO OUT AND CANVASS
UNTIL I CAN GET SOME ANSWERS.

24:21.761 --> 24:23.730
OKAY.

24:23.730 --> 24:25.698
I'M GOING WITH YOU.

24:25.698 --> 24:27.634
NO, IF I GET CAUGHT,
I'LL JUST GET DEMOTED.

24:27.634 --> 24:29.502
THEY'LL FIRE YOU.

24:29.502 --> 24:31.771
IF I'M GONNA
GET FIRED,

24:31.771 --> 24:34.073
MIGHT AS WELL BE FOR DOING
THE JOB THE RIGHT WAY.

24:34.073 --> 24:36.142
[ CAR DOOR CLOSES ]

24:36.142 --> 24:41.147
* THERE IS SOMETHING
ON YOUR MIND *

24:43.315 --> 24:47.520
* BY THE WAY YOU LOOK AT ME

24:49.355 --> 24:54.561
* THERE IS SOMETHING
ON YOUR MIND, HONEY *

24:56.529 --> 25:01.534
* BY THE WAY YOU LOOK AT ME

25:03.870 --> 25:07.306
KILL THOSE DAMN LIGHTS.

25:07.306 --> 25:09.008
* ...BRINGS HAPPINESS

25:09.008 --> 25:14.280
* OH, AND IT BRINGS MISERY

25:16.749 --> 25:18.417
* NO, NO, PLEASE...

25:18.417 --> 25:19.852
WHAT YOU WANT, ESE?

25:19.852 --> 25:21.754
YOU DON'T REMEMBER ME?

25:23.856 --> 25:26.225
WHAT ABOUT MY PARTNER?
YOU REMEMBER HIM?

25:26.225 --> 25:29.061
* ...UNDERSTAND

25:29.061 --> 25:30.563
HUH?

25:30.563 --> 25:37.704
* NO, NO, YOU DON'T HAVE TO
TELL ME, PRETTY BABY *

25:37.704 --> 25:42.942
* I THINK I UNDERSTAND

25:45.311 --> 25:50.416
* YOU WANT ME TO TRY
AND FORGET YOU *

25:50.416 --> 25:54.721
* WELL, I'LL DO THE BEST I CAN

25:54.721 --> 26:11.771
[ ENGINE TURNS OVER ]

26:11.771 --> 26:14.607
I HAD A CALLBACK
FOR "L.A. CONFIDENTIAL."

26:14.607 --> 26:15.908
[ CHUCKLES ]

26:15.908 --> 26:18.811
THEN I HEARD KIM BASINGER
WAS INTERESTED.

26:18.811 --> 26:21.580
MM.
STORY OF MY LIFE.

26:23.182 --> 26:26.786
YOU KNOW,
YOU COME HERE WITH...

26:26.786 --> 26:29.588
WITH SUCH PROMISE.

26:29.588 --> 26:32.659
AND IT GRINDS YOU UP
AND SPITS YOU OUT.

26:32.659 --> 26:35.427
AND KIM WON AN OSCAR.

26:35.427 --> 26:38.197
BUT YOU WERE GREAT
TODAY.

26:38.197 --> 26:40.566
I WAS.

26:40.566 --> 26:43.870
YOU KNOW,
SOMETHING STRANGE HAPPENS.

26:43.870 --> 26:49.041
WHEN EVERYONE'S
LOOKING AT ME...

26:49.041 --> 26:54.346
I GO INTO THIS --
THIS ZONE.

26:54.346 --> 26:58.785
I-I-I'M OUTSIDE OF MYSELF.

26:58.785 --> 27:03.555
IT'S LIKE I COULD SEE...

27:03.555 --> 27:06.558
TOOLEY KILL MIKE.

27:06.558 --> 27:09.528
LIKE YOU COULD
SEE HIM?

27:09.528 --> 27:10.596
YEAH.

27:10.596 --> 27:11.864
WAIT A MINUTE.

27:11.864 --> 27:14.366
YOU DID SEE HIM,
RIGHT?

27:14.366 --> 27:15.735
PFFT!
OF COURSE NOT.

27:15.735 --> 27:17.469
What?!
What?

27:17.469 --> 27:19.605
I WAS IN MY APARTMENT.

27:19.605 --> 27:24.110
IT WAS THAT MATT -- UH,
MATT JOHNSON ACROSS THE STREET.

27:24.110 --> 27:26.846
HE'S THE ONE WHO ACTUALLY
SAW WHAT HAPPENED.

27:26.846 --> 27:28.848
I don't believe
this shit.

27:28.848 --> 27:30.750
WHY DIDN'T JOHNSON
COME FORWARD?

27:30.750 --> 27:32.685
Meth.

27:32.685 --> 27:35.187
HE'S NOT
ALL THAT DEPENDABLE.

27:35.187 --> 27:38.024
YOU KNOW,
MIKE WAS A NICE GUY.

27:38.024 --> 27:40.727
AND THAT TOOLEY WAS
A PIECE OF SHIT.

27:40.727 --> 27:42.428
OOP! EXCUSE ME.

27:43.696 --> 27:46.132
MIKE WAS JUST TRYING
TO HELP HER.

27:46.132 --> 27:48.868
WASN'T HIS FAULT
THEY FELL IN LOVE.

27:48.868 --> 27:51.237
ALL RIGHT, SO YOU LIED
IN OPEN COURT?

27:51.237 --> 27:55.875
HEY, EVERYBODY ON THAT BLOCK
KNOWS WHAT HAPPENED.

27:55.875 --> 27:59.478
AND WHEN YOU PEOPLE CAME AROUND
ASKING QUESTIONS,

27:59.478 --> 28:01.547
I TOLD I'D SEEN IT.

28:01.547 --> 28:06.018
I WAS FLATTERED --
THIS IS TRUE.

28:06.018 --> 28:09.956
BUT THERE WAS MORE AT STAKE
THAN MY EGO.

28:09.956 --> 28:13.125
I MEAN,
SOMEBODY HAD TO STAND UP.

28:13.125 --> 28:15.261
I MEAN, IT'S THE TRUTH.

28:15.261 --> 28:16.662
HE KILLED MIKE.

28:16.662 --> 28:19.698
YOUR COP SAW HIM
WITH THE GUN.

28:19.698 --> 28:21.133
HE IS GUILTY AS HELL.

28:21.133 --> 28:23.402
UNFORTUNATELY,
SO ARE YOU.

28:23.402 --> 28:25.437
HEY!
YOU HAVE THE RIGHT
TO REMAIN SILENT.

28:25.437 --> 28:27.874
ANYTHING YOU SAY
CAN AND WILL BE USED AGAINST YOU

28:27.874 --> 28:29.308
IN A COURT OF LAW.

28:29.308 --> 28:30.409
HEY!
EXCUSE ME.

28:30.409 --> 28:31.978
CAN I GET ANOTHER
VODKA ON THE ROCKS?

28:31.978 --> 28:33.712
OH, FOR CHRIST'S SAKES.
DOUBLE, PLEASE.

28:33.712 --> 28:35.581
I DO NOT BELIEVE THIS.

28:35.581 --> 28:38.384
YEAH, WELL, IT'S GONNA BE
A LONG TIME BEFORE YOU
GET ANOTHER DRINK,

28:38.384 --> 28:41.420
SO YOU MIGHT AS WELL
GET YOUR SWERVE ON.

28:49.829 --> 28:52.031
YOU THINK I'M SCARED?

28:52.031 --> 28:56.202
UNCUFF ME,
MOTHER [BLEEP]

28:56.202 --> 28:58.838
HEY, YOU THAT WHITE BOY,
HUH?

28:58.838 --> 29:00.472
I HEARD ABOUT YOU.

29:00.472 --> 29:04.877
CRYING LIKE A BITCH,
FALLING ALL OVER THE GROUND.

29:04.877 --> 29:08.080
EVERYBODY IN THE HOOD
WAS TALKING ABOUT IT.

29:08.080 --> 29:11.951
BUT I WASN'T THERE.
IT WASN'T ME.

29:11.951 --> 29:14.854
I SWEAR ON MY GRANDMOTHER,
IT WASN'T ME.

29:14.854 --> 29:18.324
JUST LET ME GO,
MOTHER [BLEEP]

29:21.828 --> 29:23.029
[ HORN BLARES ]

29:23.029 --> 29:24.931
YOU SEEN THIS KID?

29:24.931 --> 29:26.966
WHY DON'T YOU TAKE A LOOK
AT HIM FOR TWO SECONDS?
IT'S A LITTLE KID.

29:26.966 --> 29:30.236
HAVE YOU SEEN
THIS KID BEFORE?

29:30.236 --> 29:33.705
HAVE YOU SEEN THIS KID?
THIS LITTLE BOY?

29:33.705 --> 29:37.009
HAVE YOU SEEN THIS KID
AROUND AT ALL?

29:37.009 --> 29:40.379
[ SIREN WAILING ]

29:40.379 --> 29:42.281
[ HORN HONKING ]

29:42.281 --> 29:45.517
[ MAN SPEAKS INDISTINCTLY
OVER P.A. ]

29:49.755 --> 29:52.624
PLACE IS AWFUL.

29:52.624 --> 29:55.862
YOU KNOW HOW MANY REGISTERED
SEX OFFENDERS LIVE AROUND HERE?

29:55.862 --> 29:58.297
YEAH.
YOU GET ANYTHING?

29:58.297 --> 30:00.699
NO. YOU?

30:00.699 --> 30:02.334
NO.

30:02.334 --> 30:04.904
NOTHING GLAMOROUS
ABOUT BEING A DETECTIVE.

30:04.904 --> 30:07.506
WHY DO YOU THINK
I STAYED IN PATROL?

30:10.309 --> 30:12.879
THIS CAVE...

30:12.879 --> 30:15.081
COULD BE ANYTHING.

30:15.081 --> 30:18.717
YEAH. WE GOT TO THINK
LIKE THIS KID.

30:18.717 --> 30:20.286
I MEAN,
HOW FAR COULD HE GET?

30:20.286 --> 30:24.123
YOU KNOW, A...KID THAT YOUNG,
ALONE FOR SO LONG?

30:24.123 --> 30:26.859
HE COULDN'T
HAVE GOTTEN FAR.

30:26.859 --> 30:29.795
SOMEONE AROUND HERE
HAS SEEN HIM.

30:29.795 --> 30:31.397
YOU GUYS SEEN THIS KID?

30:31.397 --> 30:33.032
Man: LET YOU KNOW
IF WE FIND SOMETHING.

30:33.032 --> 30:35.234
APPRECIATE IT.
ALL RIGHT.

30:37.436 --> 30:40.639
I DON'T KNOW.

30:40.639 --> 30:42.241
[ SCOFFS ]

30:42.241 --> 30:44.276
SOMETIMES THE ONLY SATISFACTION
YOU GET IN THIS JOB

30:44.276 --> 30:48.480
IS KNOWING YOU...
TRIED YOUR BEST.

30:50.116 --> 30:53.419
YOU KNOW WHAT?
JUST GO HOME.
I'M STAYING.

30:55.654 --> 30:57.589
[ CHUCKLES ]

30:57.589 --> 30:59.791
ALL RIGHT.
YOU TAKE THE EAST SIDE.

30:59.791 --> 31:01.894
I'LL TAKE THE WEST.
ALL RIGHT.

31:08.767 --> 31:10.602
[ ENGINE SHUTS OFF ]

31:25.817 --> 31:29.255
[ INSECTS CHIRPING ]

31:29.255 --> 31:31.357
I'M GONNA
FREE YOUR WRISTS.

31:31.357 --> 31:34.060
YOU MOVE TOO FAST,
I'LL BLOW YOU UP.

31:34.060 --> 31:35.494
[ GUN COCKS ]

31:35.494 --> 31:37.396
ALL RIGHT.

31:37.396 --> 31:39.531
[ SIGHS ]

31:43.035 --> 31:44.971
[ GRUNTS ]

31:52.711 --> 31:54.913
WHAT YOU WANT ME TO DO?

31:54.913 --> 31:57.116
I WANT YOU TO DIG.

32:09.228 --> 32:11.763
ARE THEY GONNA
LET TOOLEY GO?

32:11.763 --> 32:15.501
I DON'T KNOW. IT'S GONNA BE
A MISTRIAL AT THE VERY LEAST.

32:17.903 --> 32:21.007
EVERYONE WAS SO SCARED.

32:21.007 --> 32:23.875
NOBODY WAS GONNA DO
THE RIGHT THING.

32:23.875 --> 32:27.546
YEAH, WELL, SOMETIMES
DOING THE RIGHT THING
IS THE WRONG THING.

32:30.216 --> 32:33.285
Can you give us
a second?

32:36.555 --> 32:40.592
YOU'RE GONNA HAVE TO DIG DEEP
TO GET THROUGH THIS.

32:40.592 --> 32:44.496
YOU DON'T NEED
THAT LIQUOR CRUTCH.

32:44.496 --> 32:47.033
YOU'RE STRONGER
THAN YOU THINK.

32:49.835 --> 32:51.537
[ SIGHS ]

32:51.537 --> 32:53.505
THANK YOU.

32:53.505 --> 32:55.674
[ SIGHS ]

32:58.144 --> 33:00.979
[ SIGHS ]

33:06.085 --> 33:09.055
[ BUZZER ]

33:09.055 --> 33:11.990
[ DOOR CLOSES ]

33:20.899 --> 33:22.401
HEY.
[ GRUNTS ]

33:22.401 --> 33:24.736
YOU GUYS HAVE ANY SPARE CHANGE
I CAN HAVE?

33:24.736 --> 33:26.038
HEY, SHITBIRD.

33:26.038 --> 33:28.140
HEY!

33:28.140 --> 33:30.142
YOU FEELING OKAY,
BUDDY?

33:30.142 --> 33:33.245
YOU SEEN THIS KID?

33:35.314 --> 33:37.349
I THINK
I HAVE SEEN THIS KID.

33:37.349 --> 33:39.151
YEAH,
HE GOES AROUND SAYING

33:39.151 --> 33:40.619
"OKEY DOKEY SMOKEY"
ALL THE TIME.

33:40.619 --> 33:42.754
[ CHUCKLES ]
REMEMBER WHERE
YOU SAW HIM?

33:42.754 --> 33:45.291
NO. MNH-MNH.
NO IDEA.

33:45.291 --> 33:48.260
BUT I DO REMEMBER SEEING HIM
AT THE NEW LOFTS.

33:48.260 --> 33:50.028
THERE WAS
A SKATE PARK THERE.

33:50.028 --> 33:52.231
WHAT -- WHAT LOFTS?
YEAH.

33:52.231 --> 33:54.700
I KNOW
THE SKATE PARK.
YEAH.

33:54.700 --> 33:57.069
YEAH. OKAY.

34:05.144 --> 34:08.580
YOU THINK
THIS IS FAIR?

34:08.580 --> 34:10.182
YOU AIN'T SHIT.

34:10.182 --> 34:12.218
YOU CAN'T DO IT,
CAN YOU?

34:15.621 --> 34:17.456
I DON'T PUT IN NO WORK
NO MORE!

34:17.456 --> 34:19.258
IT WAS
ONE OF THE PEE WEES!

34:19.258 --> 34:21.360
THEY DON'T KNOW NO BETTER!
THEY DON'T RESPECT NOTHING!

34:21.360 --> 34:23.028
Sammy: IT WAS YOU.
I WAS THERE!

34:23.028 --> 34:25.797
IT WAS YOU!
I NEVER SAID I WASN'T!

34:25.797 --> 34:28.167
I STOPPED DOING DIRT
A WHILE AGO, ESE.

34:28.167 --> 34:30.369
YOU'VE OBVIOUSLY
BEEN FOLLOWING ME.

34:30.369 --> 34:33.305
I GOT A JOB.
I GOT A LIFE.

34:33.305 --> 34:37.209
I GOT A KID ON THE WAY.
I WANT TO SEE MY SON GET BORN.

34:37.209 --> 34:39.077
[ GUNSHOT ]

34:41.513 --> 34:44.550
YOU'RE THAT DUDE
ON THE OTHER SIDE OF THE GLASS.

34:44.550 --> 34:46.252
MY LAWYER TOLD ME
ABOUT YOU.

34:46.252 --> 34:48.554
YOU COULDN'T
I.D. ME THEN.

34:48.554 --> 34:51.923
WHAT MAKES YOU SURE
YOU'RE SO RIGHT NOW?

34:51.923 --> 34:53.392
[ BREATHING HEAVILY ]

34:55.394 --> 34:58.096
NATE HAD A FAMILY.
YOU HEAR ME?

34:58.096 --> 34:59.498
NATE HAD A FAMILY!

34:59.498 --> 35:02.934
WELL [BLEEP] HIS FAMILY!
AND [BLEEP] YOURS, TOO!

35:02.934 --> 35:05.604
IF YOU'RE GONNA DO IT,
DO IT!

35:05.604 --> 35:08.006
TURN AROUND.

35:08.006 --> 35:09.141
TURN AROUND!

35:21.353 --> 35:24.190
[ BREATHING HEAVILY ]

35:44.843 --> 35:49.381
I EVER SEE YOU AGAIN,
I'LL KILL YOU.

35:50.582 --> 35:52.951
YOU'RE JUST GONNA
LEAVE ME OUT HERE?

35:52.951 --> 35:54.686
HEY! HEY!

36:01.159 --> 36:03.562
[ BREATHING DEEPLY ]

36:12.170 --> 36:14.306
[ CAR DOOR SLAMS ]

36:26.952 --> 36:28.520
[ COUGHS ]

36:30.088 --> 36:32.224
[ BREATHES HEAVILY ]

36:45.671 --> 36:49.241
WHAT DO YOU WANT ME
TO SAY?

36:51.410 --> 36:54.580
YOU KNOW,
NO ONE BELIEVED ME

36:54.580 --> 36:57.783
WHEN I TOLD THEM MY DAD
WAS MOLESTING MY OLDER SISTER.

36:57.783 --> 36:59.217
[ SIGHS ]

36:59.217 --> 37:01.052
IT WASN'T UNTIL
HE RAPED AND MURDERED

37:01.052 --> 37:02.521
MY 16-YEAR-OLD GIRLFRIEND

37:02.521 --> 37:05.891
THAT ANYONE PAID ANY ATTENTION
TO ANYTHING I HAD TO SAY.

37:08.226 --> 37:11.397
THAT'S THE POWER
OF THE BADGE.

37:11.397 --> 37:13.765
WHEN WE SAY SOMETHING,
PEOPLE LISTEN.

37:15.567 --> 37:19.505
WE GOT TO SPEAK UP FOR THOSE
WHO CAN'T SPEAK FOR THEMSELVES.

37:19.505 --> 37:22.441
YEAH, BUT, JOHN,
THE GUY WAS A BASEHEAD.

37:22.441 --> 37:25.677
HOW MANY LOFTS
DID WE HIT?

37:25.677 --> 37:27.879
COFFEE'S ON ME.
[ CELLPHONE RINGS ]

37:27.879 --> 37:30.282
WE'RE GONNA NEED IT.
YOU SURE YOU'RE READY
TO GO BACK TO WORK?

37:30.282 --> 37:32.384
YEAH.
THINK WE HAVE A CHOICE?

37:32.384 --> 37:34.620
COOPER.

37:37.523 --> 37:40.492
YEAH. YEAH,
WE'LL BE THERE IN 10.

37:52.003 --> 37:53.939
[ POLICE RADIO CHATTER ]

37:53.939 --> 37:58.644
OKAY, TYRELL AND ANDY, RIGHT?
I'M OFFICER BROWN.

37:58.644 --> 38:01.046
WHY DON'T WE GET YOU GUYS
SOMETHING TO EAT, HUH?

38:13.759 --> 38:15.527
JOHN COOPER.

38:15.527 --> 38:17.363
BEN SHERMAN.

38:17.363 --> 38:19.665
I NEED A DRINK.

38:26.405 --> 38:30.175
I WAS SURPRISED
YOU CALLED.

38:30.175 --> 38:32.143
WHAT HAPPENED?

38:32.143 --> 38:34.212
COULDN'T GET WHAT YOU SAID
OUT OF MY HEAD.

38:34.212 --> 38:39.418
SO I WENT DOWN THE
SEX-OFFENDERS LIST ONE BY ONE.

38:39.418 --> 38:42.621
STOPPED HERE,
I TALKED TO HIM, AND LEFT.

38:42.621 --> 38:45.491
[ CAMERA SHUTTER CLICKING ]

38:56.301 --> 38:58.637
MAGIC CAVE.

39:18.690 --> 39:22.160
OKEY DOKEY SMOKEY.

39:22.160 --> 39:25.330
McBride: THE LETTER MENTIONS
ENCOUNTERING POLICE OFFICERS

39:25.330 --> 39:27.365
IN THE PARK
WITH MICHAEL'S PICTURE...

39:27.365 --> 39:30.936
AND MY SUBSEQUENT VISIT.

39:30.936 --> 39:34.540
HE SAID THE WALLS
WERE CLOSING IN.

39:34.540 --> 39:36.675
HOW'D YOU FIND THE BODY?

39:36.675 --> 39:40.512
HE CALLED IT IN
BEFORE HE HUNG HIMSELF.

39:40.512 --> 39:43.582
HANGED.

39:43.582 --> 39:46.217
YOU WERE RIGHT.

39:46.217 --> 39:48.687
I WAS WRONG.

40:15.781 --> 40:17.348
PETEY,
WHAT'S GOING ON?

40:17.348 --> 40:19.117
ASK MOM.

40:19.117 --> 40:22.488
[ DOOR OPENS ]

40:22.488 --> 40:26.224
WHAT'S GOING ON?

40:26.224 --> 40:30.228
UM...I'M...

40:30.228 --> 40:33.364
I'M MOVING BACK TO EL PASO,
WITH MY PARENTS,

40:33.364 --> 40:36.635
JUST UNTIL
WE FIGURE THINGS OUT.

40:36.635 --> 40:38.069
YOU'RE SELLING
THE HOUSE.

40:38.069 --> 40:41.172
[ Voice breaking ]
YEAH, UM...

40:43.509 --> 40:46.444
EVERY TIME I LOOK AROUND,
I JUST -- I SEE NATE.

40:46.444 --> 40:48.947
AND I'M DRIVING
MYSELF CRAZY.

40:48.947 --> 40:50.415
I JUST..

40:50.415 --> 40:52.017
THINGS ARE MOVING
SO FAST.

40:52.017 --> 40:54.152
I JUST --
I NEED TO SLOW DOWN.

40:55.887 --> 40:58.657
YOU UNDERSTAND,
RIGHT?

40:58.657 --> 41:03.695
* MMM, MMM

41:03.695 --> 41:05.463
* MMM, MMM

41:05.463 --> 41:06.865
YEAH.

41:06.865 --> 41:10.936
* YOU WANT ME TO TRY
AND FORGET YOU *

41:10.936 --> 41:11.937
YEAH.

41:11.937 --> 41:12.771
* WELL, I'LL DO THE BEST I CAN
